			<h3>David Holmes</h3>
			<div style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;">
				<img width="85" height="100" src="http://pandodaily.files.wordpress.com/2012/08/studio20profile.jpg?w=85&#038;h=100" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Studio20profile" />
